It's not the ID that every person has to have valid.
People who don't want to drive should turn in their driver's license.
Just bring it in or send it by registered mail to the municipal offices.
At the end of the year, the passports issued during the years 1964 and 1993 are no longer valid.
However, drivers will have to gradually change the other types of driving licence.
